TF (ngram, document, N, mode)

IDF (ngram, corpus, N, mode)


TF IDF RECORD 

  ORDER BY SELECTED COLUMNS, TF IDF RANK DESC

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Generate N-Gram Mapping Set 
  docs = set of `documents`
  corpus = name of saved `corpus` of documents
  colmap = named character vector associating `docs` and `corpus` column names
  colrank = ordered character vector of unique `corpus` column names in `colmap`

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

colmap (item_name, package_type, brand_name) ex.

